ways\"\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| 1985\n| ''[[The New Twilight Zone]]''\n| Single Guy\n| Episode: \"[[But Can She Type?]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[North and South (TV miniseries)|North and South]]''\n| Stanley Hazard\n| \n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| 1986\n| ''[[Dream West]]''\n| Lt. Archibald Gillespie \n|\n|-\n| ''[[Matlock (TV series)|Matlock]]''\n| D.A. Park\n| Episode: \"The Angel\"\n|-\n| 1987\u20131994\n| ''[[Star Trek: The Next Generation]]''\n| Commander William T. Riker\n| 176 episodes - Also portrayed transporter duplicate Lt. Thomas Riker in [[Second Chances (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Second Chances]]  \n|-\n| 1988\n| ''[[Reading Rainbow]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"The Bionic Bunny Show\"\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"| 1994\n| ''[[Wings (NBC TV series)|Wings]]''\n| Gavin Rutledge\n| Episode: \"All's Fare\"\n|-\n| ''[[Star Trek: Deep Space Nine]]''\n| Lt. Thomas Riker\n| Episode: \"Defiant\"\n|-\n| ''Journey's End: The Saga of Star Trek: The Next Generation''\n| Host\n| Documentary\n|-\n| 1994\u20131996\n| ''[[Gargoyles (TV series)|Gargoyles]]''\n| [[David Xanatos]], Coyote (voice)\n| \n|-\n|rowspan=3\"| 1995\n| ''[[Lois & Clark: The New Adventures of Superman]]''\n| Tim Lake\n| Episode: \"Don't Tug on Superman's Cape\"\n|-\n| ''[[Cybill]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"Starting on the Wrong Foot\"\n|-\n| ''[[Alien Autopsy]]: Fact or Fiction?''\n| Host/Narrator\n| \n|-\n| 1996\n| ''[[Star Trek: Voyager]]''\n| Commander William T. Riker\n| Episode: [[Death Wish (Star Trek: Voyager)|\"Death Wish\"]]\n|-\n| 1998\u20132002\n| ''[[Beyond Belief: Fact or Fiction?]]''\n| Himself \n| 45 episodes \n|-\n| 1999\n| ''[[Roswell (TV series)|Roswell]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"The Convention\"\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[3rd Rock from the Sun]]''\n| Larry McMichael\n| Episode: \"Gwen, Larry, Dick and Mary\"\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''Ghosts: Caught on Tape''\n| Narrator\n|\n|-\n| 2002\n| ''[[Futurama]]''\n| Himself (voice)\n| Episode: \"[[Where No Fan Has Gone Before]]\"\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[Star Trek: Enterprise]]''\n| Co