de: \"Episode 20\"\n|}\n\n==Directing filmography==\n\n===Feature films===\n*''[[Star Trek: Klingon]]'' (1996) \u2013 [[interactive movie]]\n*''[[Star Trek: First Contact]]'' (1996)\n*''[[Star Trek: Insurrection]]'' (1998)\n*''[[Clockstoppers]]'' (2002)\n*''[[Thunderbirds (2004 film)|Thunderbirds]]'' (2004)\n*''[[The Librarian: Return to King Solomon's Mines]]'' (2006)\n*''[[The Librarian: Curse of the Judas Chalice]]'' (2008)\n\n===Television===\n*''[[Star Trek: The Next Generation]]''\n**3.16 - [[The Offspring (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|The Offspring]] (1990)\n**4.07 - [[Reunion (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Reunion]] (1990)\n**4.21 - [[The Drumhead]] (1991)\n**5.18 - [[Cause and Effect (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Cause and Effect]] (1992)\n**6.09 - [[The Quality of Life (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|The Quality of Life]] (1992)\n**6.20 - [[The Chase (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|The Chase]] (1993)\n**7.08 - [[Attached]] (1993)\n**7.14 - [[Sub Rosa (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Sub Rosa]] (1994)\n*''[[Star Trek: Deep Space Nine]]''\n**3.02 - [[The Search (Star Trek: Deep Space Nine)|The Search, Part II]] (1994)\n**3.08 - [[Meridian (Star Trek: Deep Space Nine)|Meridian]] (1994)\n**3.13 - [[Past Tense (Star Trek: Deep Space Nine)|Past Tense, Part II]] (1995)\n*''[[Star Trek: Voyager]]''\n**2.03 - [[Projections (Star Trek: Voyager)|Projections]] (1995)\n**2.07 - [[Parturition (Star Trek: Voyager)|Parturition]] (1995)\n**2.13 - [[Prototype (Star Trek: Voyager)|Prototype]] (1996)\n*''[[Diagnosis Murder]]''\n**3.18 - [[Diagnosis: Murder (season 3)|Left-Handed Murder (1996)]]\n*''[[Roswell (TV series)|Roswell]]''\n**1.07 - [[List of Roswell episodes#Season 2(1999-2000)|River Dog (1999)]]\n**1.19 - [[List of Roswell episodes#Season 2(1999-2000)|Four Square (2000)]]\n**1.21 - [[List of Roswell episodes#Season 2(1999-2000)|The White Room (2000)]]\n**3.04 - [[List of Roswell episodes#Season 3(2001-02)|Secrets and Lies (2001)]]\n**3.08 - [[List of Rosw