eles (season 2)|2.11 - Disorder (2010)]]\n**[[NCIS: Los Angeles (season 3)|3.16 - Blye, K. (2012)]]\n**[[NCIS: Los Angeles (season 4)|4.10 - Free Ride (2012)]]\n**[[NCIS: Los Angeles (season 5)|5.02 - Impact (2013)]]\n**[[NCIS: Los Angeles (season 8)|8.10 - Sirens (2016)]]\n*''[[V (2009 series)|V]]''\n**[[List of V (2009 TV series) episodes|1.07 - John May (2010)]]\n*''[[Persons Unknown (TV series)|Persons Unknown]]''\n**1.05 - Incoming (2010)\n**1.10 - Seven Sacrifices (2010)\n**1.11 - And Then There Was One (2010)\n*''[[The Good Guys (2010 TV series)|The Good Guys]]''\n**1.09 - Don't Taze Me, Bro (2010)\n**1.16 - Silence of the Dan (2010)\n*''[[The Glades (TV series)|The Glades]]''\n**[[List of The Glades episodes#Season 1 (2010)|1.08 - Marriage Is Murder (2010)]]\n**[[List of The Glades episodes#Season 2 (2011)|2.04 - Moonlighting (2011)]]\n**[[List of The Glades episodes#Season 4 (2013)|4.02 - Shot Girls (2013)]]\n*''[[Burn Notice]]''\n**[[Burn Notice (season 4)|4.14 - Hot Property (2010)]]\n**[[Burn Notice (season 5)|5.06 - Enemy Of My Enemy (2011)]]\n**[[Burn Notice (season 5)|5.17 - Acceptable Loss (2011)]]\n**[[Burn Notice (season 6)|6.09 - Official Business (2012)]]\n**[[Burn Notice (season 7)|7.06 - All or Nothing (2013)]]\n*''[[Bar Karma]]''\n**1.09 - Three Times a Lady (2011)\n*''[[Falling Skies]]''\n**[[Falling Skies (season 3)|3.09 - Journey to Xilbalba (2013)]]\n**[[Falling Skies (season 4)|4.06 - Door Number Three (2014)]]\n**[[Falling Skies (season 5)|5.06 - Respite (2015)]]\n*''[[King & Maxwell]]''\n**1.08 - Job Security (2013)\n*''[[Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.]]''\n**[[The Well (Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.)|1.08 - The Well (2013)]]\n*''[[Switched at Birth (TV series)|Switched at Birth]]''\n**3.06 - The Scream (2014)\n**4.08 - Art Like Love is Dedication (2015)\n*''[[Hit the Floor (TV series)|Hit the Floor]]''\n**[[List of Hit the Floor episodes#Season 2 (2014)|2.03 - Behind the Back (2014)]]\n**[[List of Hit the Floor episodes#Season 2 (2014)|2.04 - Full-Court Press (2014)]]\n*''[[The Librarians (2014 TV series)|The Librarians]]''\n**[[List of The Librarians episodes#Season 1 (2014\u201315)|1.04 - And Santa's Midnight Run (2014)]]\n**[[List of The Librarians episodes#Season 1 (2014\u201315)|1.06 - And the Fables of Doom (2015)]]\n**[[List of The Librarians episodes#Season 1 (2014\u201315)|1.10 - And the Loom of Fate (2015)]]\n**[[List of The Librarians episodes#Season 2 (2015)|2.06 - And the Infernal Contract (2015)]]\n**[[List of The Librarians episodes#Season 2 (2015)|2.08 - And the Point of Salvation (2015)]]\n**3.05 - And the Tears of a Clown (2016)\n**3.06 - And the Trial of the Triangle (2016)\n**3.09 - And the Fatal Separation (2017)\n**4.04 - And the Silver Screen (2017)\n**4.06 - And the Graves of Time (2017)\n*''[[The Orville]]''\n**1.05 - Pria (2017)\n**2.12 - Sanctuary (2019)\n*''[[Star Trek: Discovery]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/tv/2017/06/27/star-trek-discovery-jonathan-frakes/|title=Star Trek: Discovery scoop: Jonathan Frakes joins as director|last=Hibberd|first=James|work=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|publisher=[[Time Inc.]]|location=United States|date=June 27, 2017|accessdate=June 27, 2017}}</ref>\n**1.10 - Despite Yourself (2018)\n**2.2 - New Eden (2019)\n**2.9 - Project Daedalus (2019)\n*''[[The Arrangement (2017 TV series)|The Arrangement]]''\n**2.9 - Truth (2018)\n*''[[The Gifted (U.S. TV series)|The Gifted]]''\n**2.13 teMpted (2019)\n*''[[Star Trek: Picard]]''\n**1.04 \"Absolute Candor\" (2020)\n**1.05 \"Stardust City Rag\" (2020)\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n* {{IMDb name|408|Jonathan Frakes}}\n* {{Tcmdb name}}\n* {{Allmovie name|24630|Jonathan Frakes}}\n* {{Twitter}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20090504131458/http://www.scifitv.com.au/Blog/2009/04/jonathan-frakes-still-number-one/ Jonathan Frakes in-depth interview] at {{URL|http://www.scifitv.com.au/blog|The SCI FI Channel Australia Blog}}\n\n{{Jonathan Frakes}}\n{{The Life Career Awa